//www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/no-doubt">No Doubt</a>已经开始为下个月在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">科切拉 (Coachella)</a>举行的重聚演出进行排练，让粉丝们先睹为快，看看他们的演出是如何形成的。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/coachella-2024-lineup-poster-talking-points-3572325">2024 年 Coachella 音乐节：今年阵容的热门话题</a></strong></li></ul><p>一月份宣布科切拉音乐节将举办该乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/no-doubt-to-reunite-for-coachella-performance-3571952">自 2015 年以来的首场演出</a>。</p><p>乐队主唱格温<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">·史蒂芬妮 (Gwen Stefani)</a>在她的 Instagram 帐户上分享了一段乐队表演的视频，视频从她的舞蹈开始，然后她拿着相机，在其他成员演奏时依次走到他们面前。</p><p>看看下面的视频： </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C5E2Ss9vXTG/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g s