iv></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center; margin-bottom: 24px;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 224px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 144px;"></div></div><p></p><p style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; line-height:17px; margin-bottom:0; margin-top:8px; overflow:hidden; padding:8px 0 7px; text-align:center; text-overflow:ellipsis; white-space:nowrap;"> <a href="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5HVa0hS-VD/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" style=" color:#c9c8cd; font-family:Arial,sans-serif; font-size:14px; font-style:normal; font-weight:normal; line-height:17px; text-decoration:none;" target="_blank">Lizzo (@lizzobeeating) 分享的帖子</a></p></div></blockquote><p><script async src="//platform.instagram.com/en_US/embeds.js"></script></p><p>此前，利佐请求<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzos-request-to-dismiss-her-sexual-harrassment-lawsuit-denied-by-judge-3581843">驳回即将提起的性骚扰和歧视诉讼，</a>但遭到法官拒绝。</p><p>去年八月，这位音乐家被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-sued-by-backup-dancers-for-sexual-harassment-and-creating-hostile-work-environment-3476570">指控在阿姆斯特丹的一家脱衣舞俱乐部营造敌对的工作环境和性骚扰</a>。作为回应，利佐写道，她“受伤了”，并称<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-responds-to-sexual-harassment-lawsuit-im-hurt-3477714">这些指控是“虚假的”。</a>此后，律师们审查了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lawyers-reviewing-new-complaints-from-more-of-lizzos-former-dancers-3480608">其他伴舞演员的更多投诉</a>，而利佐<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-named-in-new-bullying-and-harassment-lawsuit-from-fashion-designer-3502090">在九月的一项新诉讼中被点名，由一位前发型师提起，</a>她<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-requests-to-dismiss-meritless-harassment-and-discrimination-lawsuit-3561059">进一步提出驳回诉讼</a>。</p><p>现在，洛杉矶法官裁定此案将全面进行审判。最初，Lizzo 的律师于 9 月根据加州反 SLAPP 法规（“针对公众参与的战略诉讼”） <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-asks-judge-to-dismiss-ridiculous-harassment-lawsuit-3506381">提出“全部”驳回诉讼</a>。这座雕像旨在迅速驳回威胁言论自由的诉讼。利佐的律师辩称，她的伴舞试图让她“闭嘴”。</p><p>作为回应，法官裁定该诉讼不符合反 SLAPP 立法。虽然他确实驳回了伴舞演员提出的某些指控，包括指控利佐<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-body-not-trend-im-so-much-more-than-that-2600048">尽管多年来一直倡导身体积极性，但还是</a>因肥胖而羞辱了一名舞者，但他裁定案件的其余部分可以继续审理。</p><p>尽管如此，利佐表示她正在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-teases-new-music-the-magic-is-back-3574089">创作新音乐</a>，并表示她觉得“魔力又回来了”。</p><p>利佐此前曾<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-im-working-on-music-myself-trust-issues-with-the-world-3542544">在 11 月份</a>表示，她也一直在花时间解决自己以及与世界的信任问题。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/lizzo-responds-to-being-dragged-online-i-quit-3611344">Lizzo 回应网上“被拖”的帖子：“I QUIT”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 RAYE 透露她与碧昂丝在《牛仔卡特》中共同创作了《RIIVERDANCE》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-reveals-that-she-co-wrote-beyonces-riiverdance-on-cowboy-carter-3611049?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=raye-reveals-that-她与人合写了《牛仔卡特》中的碧昂丝·河舞Damian JonesFri, 29 Mar 2024 21:47:25 +0000 Music NewsNewsCountryPop https://www.nme.com/?p=3611049 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="雷伊和碧昂斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “牛仔卡特日快乐”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-reveals-that-she-co-wrote-beyonces-riiverdance-on-cowboy-carter-3611049">RAYE 的帖子透露，她在《Cowboy Carter》中与人合写了碧昂丝的《RIIVERDANCE》，该歌曲</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="雷伊和碧昂斯" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/03/2024_raye_beyonce_getty_2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/raye">雷伊</a>透露，她与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beyonce">碧昂斯</a>合作创作了一首歌曲《牛仔卡特》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/raye-polydor-new-album-hard-out-here-3260215">RAYE：“我成了‘租一首诗’。人们知道我的歌，但他们不了解我”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brit-awards-2024-winners-nominations-list-3595742">六次全英音乐奖得主</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/raye-polydor-new-album-hard-out-here-3260215">此前曾为 Queen Bey 创作过歌曲，</a>其中最著名的是 2019 年的《Bigger》，以及为<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/mabel">Mabel</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>创作的歌曲，</p><p>现在，她在 Instagram 上庆祝今天发行的新唱片的发行，并分享了她为这张唱片做出贡献的“荣誉”。</p><p>雷伊分享了一段她跟着歌曲唱歌的片段（您可以在下面收听），她写道：“牛仔卡特日快乐。能够为这张美丽的专辑贡献我的小作品，以及继续激励我们所有人的@beyonce，我感到非常荣幸。第 23 首：RIIVERDANCE，由我共同创作，找到了我在 21 岁生日时为这个特殊场合买的破旧牛仔帽。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C5G6_eCIoLM/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; fle