nces-cowboy-carter-3610940">对这张专辑做出了评价</a>，她将其描述为<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/azealia-banks-slams-beyonces-cowboy-carter-as-white-women-cosplay-3607552">“白人女性角色扮演”</a> ，同时还表示<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/azealia-banks-tells-beyonce-youre-setting-yourself-up-to-be-ridiculed-again-over-new-country-album-3586845">她觉得这位歌手“让自己受到嘲笑”</a> 。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/kt-tunstall-reacts-to-azealia-banks-singling-her-out-on-beyonces-cowboy-carter-3611040">这位歌手兼作曲家</a>表示，如果唱片中有<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/kt-tunstall">KT Tunstall 的</a>特色内容， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/azealia-banks-personally-would-have-jumped-out-of-seat-for-a-kt-tunstall-appearance-on-beyonces-cowboy-carter-3610940">她一定会“从座位上跳起来”</a> ，随后她开玩笑地回应道：“公平地说，我会 100% 从沙发上跳起来。”</p><p>与此同时，在破纪录地赢得全英音乐奖后，雷伊最近<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-youve-got-these-ceos-and-big-label-execs-living-in-their-fat-huge-chelsea-mansions-while-songwriters-you-are-profiting-off-are-broke-3600564">猛烈抨击行业高管，称他们在为自己谋取巨额利润的同时，却向词曲作者支付过低的报酬</a>。她还在<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/saturday-night-live"><em>《周六夜现场》</em></a>中<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-confirmed-to-perform-on-snl-with-kristen-wiig-3601019">表演</a>。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/raye-reveals-that-she-co-wrote-beyonces-riiverdance-on-cowboy-carter-3611049">RAYE 的帖子透露，她在《Cowboy Carter》中与人合写了碧昂丝的《RIIVERDANCE》，该歌曲</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
